{"id": "wat-pratu-pa", "name": "วัดประตูป่า", "nameRoman": "Wat Pratu Pa", "lat": 18.620278, "lng": 99.004722, "heritage": "registered Thai historic site", "status": "active", "founded": "", "description": "Buddhist temple in Lamphun province, Thailand", "summary": {"text": "วัดประตูป่า เป็นวัดราษฎร์สังกัดคณะสงฆ์ฝ่ายมหานิกาย ตั้งอยู่ในตำบลประตูป่า อำเภอเมืองลำพูน จังหวัดลำพูน ที่ตั้งวัดมีเนื้อที่ 4 ไร่ และที่ดินของวัดจำนวน 8 แปลงอยู่รอบบริเวณวัด จำนวน 16.1 ไร่ เป็นที่ตั้งของโรงเรียนวัดประตูป่ารวมอยู่ด้วยในปัจจุบัน", "title": "วัดประตูป่า", "url": "https://th.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B9%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%B2", "lang": "th", "license": "CC BY-SA 4.0", "licenseUrl": "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/"}, "province": "Lamphun", "district": "", "street": "", "phone": "", "website": "", "email": "", "facebook": "", "openingHours": "", "confidence": "crawled", "photos": [{"thumb": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/83/%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%81%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%A0%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%8C%E0%B9%82%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%93_%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B9%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%B2.jpg/960px-%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%81%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%A0%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%8C%E0%B9%82%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%93_%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B9%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%B2.jpg", "author": "นายพิชิต คำบุรี", "license": "CC BY-SA 3.0", "licenseUrl": "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0", "source": "https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%81%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%A0%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%8C%E0%B9%82%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%